title: 820-2879 gren light no fan spin. missing 5v
message:
This old machine is not iCore, so it doesn't power on by itself when charger is plugged in.
Toggle SMC_ONOFF_L and check for any reaction at PM_PWRBTN_L and PM_SLP_Sx_L signals.
3V3_S5 and 0V9_S5 are both required before starts...
